snippet.title: ✨Stella Sora Gameplay Trailer✨
snippet.description:
Legend speaks of a wish granted by the Monoliths equally to anyone who ascends to their top. After a thousand-year slumber, you, the Tyrant, bearer of trust and hope through the ages, have finally reawakened. Lead the brave on a journey to conquer the Monoliths and forge new possibilities.

Ascend, and seek the truth.

——
Stella Sora is a top-down, light-action adventure game developed by YOSTAR.

Pre-registration is now available for Stella Sora on our official website!
For the latest information on Stella Sora, find us here:

Stella Sora Official Website: 
https://stellasora.global/

Official Discord Server:
https://discord.gg/hNDKSCuD8G

Official X Account:
https://x.com/StellaSoraEN

Official Facebook Page:
https://www.facebook.com/StellaSoraEN/

Official YouTube Account:
https://www.youtube.com/@StellaSoraEN

#StellaSora #Yostar
